spec_data.Name: php-fig-link-util
spec_data.Description:
This package includes common utilities to assist with implementing
PSR-13 [1].

Note that it is not intended as a complete PSR-13 implementation, only
a partial implementation to make writing other implementations easier.

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/Fig/Link/autoload.php

[1] http://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-13/
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 07:36:24 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Common utility implementations for HTTP links
